      <div class="tab-panel" id="panel-2">
        <div class="artwork-guide">
          <div class="artwork-intro">
            <h3>Artwork & File Requirements</h3>
            <p>To ensure the best print quality for your {product.name}, please follow these artwork guidelines when preparing your design files.</p>
          </div>
